## What's New (User Facing)
Admin Dashboard: View lot/slot status, basic slot management, and admin controls for parking flow.
Check-in / Check-out flow: Admin can check vehicles in/out and the system computes parking fees.
Slot availability + reservation core: Initial reservation/availability logic is implemented to support booking states.

## Work Summary (Developer Facing)

For this sprint, we implemented a Smart Parking Management System via Flask. We delivered check in/check out with fee calculations. We implemented a schema for rates/sessions/payments/reservation states. We also created a dashboard at /admin with lot/slot status, check in/check out controls, and overall basic slot management. 


## Unfinished Work

Although Sprint 1 established the project foundation, there are still several features missing. The current work is strongest on the admin-side prototype, core reservation logic, and check-in/check-out flow, but the full driver-facing experience still needs to be finished. That includes end-to-end user registration/login, role enforcement, and a polished reservation workflow are not fully implemented yet. Payment support has been partially prepared through schema and state handling, but the complete payment process and receipt/history flow still need more work. In addition, the UI needs refinement, more edge cases must be handled, and broader testing is needed to improve stability before the next sprint.

